The paper deals with joint source-channel coding, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). It also discusses the coordination capabilities of devices in decentralized networks, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of power control and channel allocation, which are topics in multimedia systems (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the optimization of a utility function, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG).
